Class DisjointSetUnion<E>

java.lang.Object

          com.complexible.common.collect.DisjointSetUnion<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>
public class DisjointSetUnion<E>
extends AbstractSet<E>

A mutable union of disjoint sets. This class guarantees to obey the Set contract only of the outer code guarantees that the sets are indeed disjoint and does not attempt to add elements which already exist in the union.

Author:
Pavel Klinov
